333
00:32:15,165 --> 00:32:19,626
All right, so if we have - these are
Venn diagrams, as you remember...

334
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:23,463
If we have A and B intersecting,...

335
00:32:23,547 --> 00:32:25,632
..and A and B...

336
00:32:25,716 --> 00:32:28,760
