343
00:33:07,965 --> 00:33:11,052
Um, he was nice.

344
00:33:11,135 --> 00:33:13,429
It was really sad when he died.

345
00:33:16,015 --> 00:33:18,976
Oh, my gosh.
I can't believe I just said that.

346
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:21,102
I am so sorry.

