green pamphlets were distributed.

352
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:53,676
(teacher) We thought green was cheerful,
but not too cheerful.

353
00:33:53,759 --> 00:33:55,803
Certainly better than red.

354
00:33:55,928 --> 00:34:00,724
