372
00:35:15,088 --> 00:35:18,467
Do you wanna know what happened?
Smell my fingers, man.

373
00:35:18,967 --> 00:35:21,220
Nah, she didn't talk about Cecilia.

374
00:35:21,303 --> 00:35:24,514
We weren't exactly talking,
