407
00:38:00,331 --> 00:38:03,501
I never got over that girl. Never.

408
00:38:05,461 --> 00:38:09,298
I mean... you know,
I loved a lot of ladies, but not like that.

409
00:38:09,382 --> 00:38:11,509
That was real.

410
00:38:12,218 --> 00:38:16,389
I'll never forget the first time I saw her.
